KitKat::

She was greathful to the bot for saving her skin.  She could feel 
her body regenerating in the chamber.  She was starting to fall 
asleep when her internal program alarms went off.  She was being 
reprogrammed.  Tried as she could to fight, her power levels were 
not high enough to have her fail safe programs put up the firewalls 
and protect her main programs.  She was being reprogrammed to have 
her loyalties for this new bot whom she had never met yet.  She 
could feel the program download into her mainframe.  Her loyalty was 
now for Hydras.  Soon, she would emerge from the chamber.
